{"tid":1818142,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"內建 10nm++ Tiger Lake CPU!!  Intel 要摺了?! 展示全新可摺疊概念機","createTime":"2020-01-09T15:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T01:09:51.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7bd267d14dc9e8ca03736f774fb309829d48a6","tid":1818142,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"「可摺疊」的手機潮近年又再興起，不過與之前的「摺機」完全不同，新型的「摺機」如 Samsung 最新推出的 Galaxy Fold 就是在屏幕中間具有「可摺疊」的功能，可以帶來另類的觀看及操控體驗，而在 CES 2020 大會上，Intel 帶來了一款「可摺疊」的概念 PC，這款概念產品名為「Horseshoe Bend」，尺寸與 12 吋的行動電腦相若，配有折疊式觸控屏，展開平放時就會變成一個 17.3 吋 4:3 的屏幕，提供兩種不同的使用模式。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 展示的全新「可摺疊」行動電腦名為「Horseshoe Bend」，相比 Lenovo X1 Fold 擁有更大的尺寸。「Horseshoe Bend」兩組 OLED 顯示屏幕的中央連為一體，在「展開」的使用模式下，會變成一個 17.3 吋 4:3 的屏幕，當以一定角度放置在桌上使用時，就可以當作一個屏幕方式顯示。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/01/source/07201340201078152099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F01%2Fsource%2F07201340201078152099.jpg&h=8731be4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在改成「摺疊」的使用模式時，「Horseshoe Bend」就與 12 吋的行動電腦相若。此外，「Horseshoe Bend」支援觸控操作及外接無線鍵盤，還有一個 Surface 風格的支架，因此可以在與無線鍵盤配對時充分利用整個顯示屏的尺寸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/01/source/07201346261006092863.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F01%2Fsource%2F07201346261006092863.gif&h=b1144325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/01/source/07201345252132093368.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F01%2Fsource%2F07201345252132093368.gif&h=651cc49b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ce9b8a8ff71ed80fac79313d7839dbfce4e9e3c","tid":1818142,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"「Horseshoe Bend」是基於 Intel 全新 10nm Tiger Lake 架構的處理器，在 CES 2020 現場的概念產品運行了常規的 Windows 10 作業系統，但相信專為「可摺疊」PC 打造的 Windows 10X 更加適合此類產品。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 官方表示，將會積極推動「可摺疊」形態的行動電腦，並希望與多家製造商合作，或許不久之後就會像「可摺疊」手機一樣，投放市場，並逐漸成為主流。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/18893/CES_2020內建_10nm%2B%2B_Tiger_Lake_CPU__Intel_要摺了_展示全新可摺疊概念機\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F18893%2FCES_2020%E5%85%A7%E5%BB%BA_10nm%252B%252B_Tiger_Lake_CPU__Intel_%E8%A6%81%E6%91%BA%E4%BA%86_%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%AF%E6%91%BA%E7%96%8A%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E6%A9%9F&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=af0dcb5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/18893/CES_2020內建_10nm%2B%2B_Tiger_Lake_CPU__Intel_要摺了_展示全新可摺疊概念機</a>"},{"pid":"09560c712600909b463703b392702fb738a5cdca","tid":1818142,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"究竟windows 出下一代先定煙條出下一代先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0c5ccccfd09c09b3352f9cf0ade46da2b8f9b1","tid":1818142,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"Intel Yes!"},{"pid":"62d77053b9fbd0cf033a736fc62ab4b8efb9aecd","tid":1818142,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09560c712600909b463703b392702fb738a5cdca","tid":1818142,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"究竟windows 出下一代先定煙條出下一代先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"煙條年年都出下一代<br />\n都係14nm咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3815b75780fde536a65fcdfa20b8621ea51c64","tid":1818142,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d77053b9fbd0cf033a736fc62ab4b8efb9aecd","tid":1818142,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09560c712600909b463703b392702fb738a5cdca","tid":1818142,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"究竟windows 出下一代先定煙條出下一代先呢<i